{"tid":483933,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)我隻貓病咗三個幾月.....","createTime":"2017-11-29T15:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T05:21:28.000Z","uid":49387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6696973c63e049ad3c23502c7c8c7633e6f10b9e","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"八月帶咗隻貓去沖涼剪毛<br />\n幾日後發現佢好唔對路 呼吸好似人哮喘咁gugu聲 眼紅又腫 就帶咗佢睇醫生<br />\n醫生話係傷風 開咗藥 眼藥水個啲<br />\n但係食咗個幾月都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有好轉過一排又差返<br />\n所以轉咗醫生 呢個醫生話佢只係鼻塞 <br />\n肺同腦個啲冇事 又開咗藥<br />\n而家日日係屋企同佢吸氣 吊鹽水 餵藥都冇好轉<br />\n仲好似越黎越差 唔食野 瘦咗好多<br />\n唔會自己去柯屎尿 瀨係屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗 可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14551fc3245233f00dd9228b3c4beda1dd912694","tid":483933,"uid":148197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"諗起都心痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去開荃灣寵物醫院 個醫生幾好架"},{"pid":"2976266f50157fb42d24ec0c8edff2b977432f3c","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起都心痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去開荃灣寵物醫院 個醫生幾好架</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以介紹比我 而家個醫生睇多排唔得就轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5be70f431321c8f3f58e251414527bdf81b1a8a","tid":483933,"uid":148197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/233448_28339efcca79274489ef7c52694aaf7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F233448_28339efcca79274489ef7c52694aaf7a.jpg&h=13d77a45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n個鐘醫生出名好架 網上都聲譽唔錯 好錫動物<br />\n雖然可能都幫唔到咩 但希望佢幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce03a96988e4ca6e04a0a0a66a927e2ab67600c","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/233448_28339efcca79274489ef7c52694aaf7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F233448_28339efcca79274489ef7c52694aaf7a.jpg&h=13d77a45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n個鐘醫生出名好架 網上都聲譽唔錯 好錫動物<br />\n雖然可能都幫唔到咩 但希望佢幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f4c4d94e5c740d9f8e792b8506137cc64ec441","tid":483933,"uid":148197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"不過佢好似有幾個醫生 但鐘醫生應該最好 你預約嗰陣問下"},{"pid":"7b6da8062939722e968b98eb68085f508bded84a","tid":483933,"uid":142433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476013612c37ddc5de6122a15d297e34008bf4ea","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過佢好似有幾個醫生 但鐘醫生應該最好 你預約嗰陣問下</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該曬你"},{"pid":"fd7bae09ae337a15c69bb5e4323015c989200ca3","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b46e589196533182915007a170ca918f856fe01","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"999fac6bec9cc17871ed76db14ec2b5de21292cf","tid":483933,"uid":160311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"佢有冇發燒呀？會唔會係貓瘟"},{"pid":"a43781e258ef10d914e800ae3d3ae936fa53a069","tid":483933,"uid":160311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"醫生話冇事前提有冇照過x ray 或者超聲波個啲？"},{"pid":"81ff7e04885974fb6af29f149587b636644c49ea","tid":483933,"uid":42598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"我2隻仔都係鐘醫生睇嫁<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"668be778fb3d9ef125eb969d37c1d04de5e4c3a7","tid":483933,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生話冇事前提有冇照過x ray 或者超聲波個啲？</blockquote><br />\n冇發燒 <br />\n醫生話照xray要打麻醉針 但佢身體太弱受唔到 所以冇得照住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}